{"tid":1785634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［提醒］香港人頂住","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T14:35:32.000Z","uid":99107,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19d9f93020838048a7c9dabf1992d420cad1ff3b","tid":1785634,"uid":99107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"呢半年，辛苦大家嘅付出，相信無人會知雨傘後嘅香港人會進步得咁快。要勇氣，有勇氣；要善良，有善良；要智慧，我哋都有。我哋經歷咗好多，亦都失去咗好多，我地對未來無咩掌握，但我哋學識咗努力現在、學識去堅持。<br />\n<br />\n相信林鄭見完習近平，又會有一連串行動。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港人記住：<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無論對家開咩條件，只要唔係回應五大訴求，談判都無需要。</span>我哋要好alert 對家嘅一舉一動，或者佢地會加強分化、加強抹黑，甚或軟硬兼施，面對呢啲計謀，我哋只需要做嘅就係點都要令對家回應同實踐五大訴求，只需要記嘅就係過世嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n知道呢段時間更加考驗大家嘅勇氣同智慧，但我深信香港人唔怕。成功之後，可以煲底見，過世手足可以真相大白，世界各地嘅手足都可以返呢個「家」，我哋下一代可以體驗到民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，繼續智取！一齊入公會！勝利不遠！<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港。"},{"pid":"030cdce43af044d93b0f1a8a84e47aacfd30b915","tid":1785634,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"4fc8411609d6102bd27d603b33d6fa56c29e48f2","tid":1785634,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"621 721 831 新屋嶺"},{"pid":"eb946013414f6b1a2a48b823f068963e6bce604a","tid":1785634,"uid":271857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"30萬食沙律。"},{"pid":"1de40b7d145e23020ba817fedbc0bb1265b1f7a8","tid":1785634,"uid":251769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja88Na2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja88Na2.jpg&h=543efee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmRJ7hx.jpg&h=a821da85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咤叱歌曲投票link 👇👇👇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://usca.my903.com/mobile/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusca.my903.com%2Fmobile%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7oCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=a434c72a\" target=\"_blank\">https://usca.my903.com/mobile/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkEv0ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkEv0ur.jpg&h=03b9c910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49757f5c1d06b7d11b531bccc45ac30eed5e8030","tid":1785634,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"香港人頂埋佢"},{"pid":"9529024f809568d4ebe875688b3b0ef06a735930","tid":1785634,"uid":65178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:57:01.000Z","msg":"士氣post要推"},{"pid":"cdc65b9c4d08539203fcb070384d580a74fc2ccf","tid":1785634,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:57:46.000Z","msg":"有𥌓光，有希望，香港人加油"},{"pid":"29d720c37c15685a400f2dbf94a285c201c4c152","tid":1785634,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"621 721 831 新屋嶺"},{"pid":"343dcb9215bdb2c9daa5ba71bed3543a692d70c7","tid":1785634,"uid":318497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聲援維吾爾族人權集會</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公海: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat